4. NUMA topology mismatch

Your node has:

Detected NUMA nodes: 2

Telecom CNFs often require:

CPUs

Hugepages

SRIOV VF


all from SAME NUMA socket.

If:

VF from NUMA1

CPUs from NUMA0

hugepages from NUMA0


then app exits silently.


